* AKFAvatar 0.19.0

  - new program lua-akfavatar
  - some ignorable Unicode characters are ignored now
  - pager can handle binary junk better
  - filechooser: path can be entered manually
  - filechooser: on windows ask for drive letter only when 
    going beyond the root directory
  - ./configure: experimental support for --host=mingw and --host=x86
  - avt_free_audio(): when that sound is playing, stop it

  API changes:
   avt_tell, avt_tell_mb: new functions
   avt_markup: new function
